          "action_timeout": 180,
          "chat_messages": [
            {
              "content": "Role: Data Extraction Specialist.\n\n\nTask: Parse the provided RSS JSON data to find the relative URL for a specific firmware version.\n\n\nTarget Version: $activity.definition_activity_02TFLXYEJOKSO60CO3iVE3GUYojDi7gbgpO.output.jsonpath_queries.Version Short Name$ \n\nExtraction Logic:\n\n\nNavigate: $activity.definition_activity_02T3DGSES6WAC7aU9QPLta1yZB3tjQmSpFk.output.response_body$ array.\nSearch: Iterate through every item in that array.\nMatch: Look for the item where the description field contains the exact target version string.\nExtract: Once found, take the value of the link field for that item.\n\nTransformation Rule:\n\n\nConvert the absolute URL to a relative URL.\nRemove https://community.meraki.com \n\nOutput Constraints:\n\n\nReturn only the raw relative URL string.\nDo not use markdown code blocks or backticks.\nDo not include any introductory text, explanations, or quotes.",
              "role": "user"
